1. As a time pressed computer user
So that I can quickly find web sites I recently bookmarked
I would like to see a reverse chronological list of links on the site homepage

2. As a time pressed computer user
So that I can bookmark websites that interest me
I would like to be able to add new links to the site homepage

3. As a time pressed computer user
So that I can organize my links better
I would like to add tags to the links I added on the site homepage

4. As a time pressed computer user
So that I can navigate through my collection of links quickly
I would like to be able to filter through my links via a tags